Introduction

VAV is a six-member boy group formed by A team Entertainment. They made their debut on October 31, 2015, with the mini-album 'Under the Moonlight'. Over the years, the group experienced several lineup changes, with new members joining and others departing between 2016 and 2017. In March 2023, member Baron left the group.

On February 29, 2024, the group's contract with A Team Entertainment ended. However, the members confirmed on March 3rd that they have not disbanded and will continue as a group, asking fans to look forward to their future.
